entry.title: U.S.-Saudi Tensions Ease as Concerns About Iran Grow
entry.content: The Biden administration has dropped threats to retaliate against Saudi Arabia for an oil-production cut last year and is moving to step up security coordination to counter Iran, U.S. and Saudi officials said.
